", "text": "Many analysts expect Hormuz to return to pre-war normal\n\n@TheStudyofWar argues the opposite \n\nIt's using the ceasefire to create permanent leverage\n\nThe probability of normalized flows is therefore almost zero \n\nBecause that would reduce Iran's leverage to almost zero\n\n#OOTT #Oil #Hormuz #Iran #Geop", "time": "02:13", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 7897, "likes": 55, "replies": 5, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069968057380802568", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069968057380802568", "text": "The IRGC Navy just rejected the Oman-IMO Hormuz transit plan\n\nAnalysts may think the Hormuz crisis is over\n\nIran disagrees.\n\nWithout an ongoing crisis or threat of crisis, Iran has no power except as a fee taker\n\n#OOTT #Oil #Hormuz #Iran #Shipping", "time": "02:16", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 6632, "likes": 54, "replies": 9, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069968888884760728", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069968888884760728", "text": "Watch the Hormuz inflows, not just the outflows.\n\nMore ships are leaving Hormuz\n\nFar fewer are returning\n\nThe traffic jam is clearing but cars are avoiding the freeway\n\nThat's not a return to normal—it's lingering caution\n\n#OOTT #Oil #Hormuz #Shipping #Energy", "time": "02:20", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 10011, "likes": 120, "replies": 6, "retweets": 25, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069981725275430973", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069981725275430973", "text": "Rabobank's @TheMichaelEvery offers the best strategic view of the Iran crisis so far\n\nThis isn't peace—it's an armistice with multiple unresolved fault lines\n\nThat armistice could last quite a while IMO but Israel could blow it up\n#OOTT #Oil #Hormuz #Iran #Geopolitics https://t.co/UFbBdz0k2D", "time": "03:11", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 20418, "likes": 34, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069983679938527509", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069983679938527509", "text": "Scott Bessent may have revealed the administration's real theory, writes Molly Schwartz\n\n\"We didn't have regime change, but we changed the regime\"\n\nIf that's true, the Iran deal isn't surrender—it's a wager that coercion changed Tehran's behavior. \n\nWhat nonsense.\n\n #Iran #OOTT #Geopolitics #Oil #Tr", "time": "03:19", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 4241, "likes": 85, "replies": 9, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2069988209124057548", "url": "https://x.com/PrestigeReFini1/status/2069988209124057548", "text": "Way oversold reserves drained tankers that won’t return through the strait but oil prices sunk \nSomething not right here. Coiling that spring #oott", "time": "03:37", "author": "PrestigeReFini1", "author_name": "kraken", "followers": 205, "views": 2396, "likes": 37, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2070064384353685685", "url": "https://x.com/cbjom/status/2070064384353685685", "text": "Next war in the Middle East will be an oil price war, not the other kind of war.\n\n#OOTT", "time": "08:39", "author": "cbjom", "author_name": "Crudehead🛢", "followers": 17544, "views": 21089, "likes": 73, "replies": 8, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 15, "labels": null}, {"id": "2070064491660820583", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2070064491660820583", "text": "#China to raise refined fuel export allowance in July, sources say #oott https://t.co/kIfuZULolp", "time": "08:40", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4076, "likes": 11, "replie